blog.description: HIYA FELLOW SWIFTIES About me: Hi i'm Millie i'm 21 years old from England i'm huge Swiftie have been since ''Tim Mcgraw'' im always dying my hair crazy colours depending on my mood i wear bright Yellow boots with dresses and chockers alot yes i'm a little odd i play Guitar have since i was 9 and paino from the age of 11 i love Animals and i'm a Vegetarian my favourite Animals are Sloth's (omg they are so cute i can't ) and Cat's i had a cat who was my best friend called Barry Allen...Yes just like Taylor i name my pets after my favourite tv characters no shame my favourite food is Cheese Pizza i can't get enough i love it i study photography and english college so i love to make and creat things and write alot i'm always buying art supplies and pretty fabric and i've lost count of how many journals i have it's a problem i really try my best to stay happy and positive all the time which someday's it's really hard as i don't have any friends and suffer from depression panic and anxiety attacks and extreme paranoia mostly caused by bullying but my family and Taylor get me through those tough times i hope through Taylor and our amazing fandom we can all help eachotther and be friends i hope i can meet some friends maybe a pen pal ;)  and we can all fangirl over Taylor and Cat's and pizza together lol :D  i'm lame but seriously never ever be afraid to message me if you need to talk anytime or just fancy a little chit chat lol so british love you Taylor and Swifties
